 <section id="capacity-calc" class="mb-16">
 <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-brandBlue uppercase italic mb-6">5. How Do You Calculate Power Bank Capacity for Your Devices?</h2>
 <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">Pick the right capacity by knowing your device's battery size, use habits, and travel needs. This data-based method makes sure you never run out of power or spend too much on extra capacity.</p>
 
 <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 mb-6">
 <h3 class="font-black text-slate-900 uppercase mb-4">Step 1: Know Your Device Battery Size</h3>
 <div class="overflow-x-auto">
 <table class="w-full text-sm">
 <thead>
 <tr class="border-b border-slate-200">
 <th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-black text-brandBlue uppercase">Device Type</th>
 <th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-black text-brandBlue uppercase">Typical Battery</th>
 <th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-black text-brandBlue uppercase">Notes</th>
 </tr>
 </thead>
 <tbody class="text-slate-600">
 <tr class="border-b border-slate-100">
