 <section id="sourcing-china" class="mb-16">
 <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-brandBlue uppercase italic mb-6">8. How to Source Power Banks from China (B2B)</h2>
 <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">China is still the world's top maker of consumer electronics, including power banks. Knowing the <a href="https://www.trade.gov/knowledge-product/exporting-power-banks" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-brandOrange hover:underline">sourcing landscape</a> helps you find quality products at good prices while avoiding common traps. For a curated list of verified suppliers, see our <a href="/blog/top-power-bank-manufacturers-china" class="text-brandOrange hover:underline">guide to the top power bank manufacturers in China</a>.</p>
 
 <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 mb-6">
 <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4">When checking power bank makers, look past unit price. Cell quality, certs, QC steps, and fast replies all matter. They affect your total cost and product success.</p>
 <h3 class="font-black text-slate-900 uppercase mb-4">Key Sourcing Considerations</h3>
 <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
 <div>
 <h4 class="font-black text-brandBlue uppercase text-sm mb-2">MOQ (Minimum Order Quantity)</h4>
 <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Factory MOQs typically range from 500-5,000 units. Some suppliers offer lower MOQs for standard products. <a href="/contact" class="text-brandOrange hover:underline">Contact us</a> to discuss your volume requirements.</p>
 </div>
 <div>
 <h4 class="font-black text-brandBlue uppercase text-sm mb-2">Lead Times</h4>
 <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Standard products: 7-14 days. Custom OEM/ODM: 30-60 days including tooling and sampling. Shipping via sea freight adds 20-35 days depending on destination.</p>
 </div>
 <div>
 <h4 class="font-black text-brandBlue uppercase text-sm mb-2">Pricing Factors</h4>
 <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Component quality (brand cells vs generic), certifications required, custom branding, packaging specifications, and order volume all affect final pricing.</p>
 </div>
 <div>
 <h4 class="font-black text-brandBlue uppercase text-sm mb-2">Payment Terms</h4>
 <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Standard terms: 30% deposit, 70% balance before shipment. L/C available for orders over $50,000. Alibaba Trade Assurance recommended for first-time orders.</p>
 </div>
 </div>
 </div>

 <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">Before placing your first order, decide on the right manufacturing model — see our <a href="/blog/oem-vs-odm-guide" class="text-brandOrange font-bold underline">OEM vs ODM guide for charger brands</a>. Then verify the factory itself with the <a href="/blog/factory-verification-checklist" class="text-brandOrange font-bold underline">factory verification checklist</a> before signing.</p>

 <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">According to MarketsAndMarkets, the global power bank market is expected to reach $18.5 billion by 2028, growing at a CAGR of 8.2%. This sustained growth is driven by increasing smartphone penetration, remote work trends, and the global transition to USB-C across all device categories, creating ongoing opportunities for brands that invest in quality power bank products.</p>

